column6:
Killeen Townhomes specializes in temporary housing offering month to month furnished homes with a minimum of 14 days.

Have more space with a fully stocked kitchen and all your appliances.

Make your stressful move a bit easier.

 * All Utilities Included with WiFi and Cable
 * All Appliances with Washer, Dryer,
 * 2 pets of 60 lbs accepted ($200 one-time fee per pet+$30/monthly per pet pet rent)
* Co-Worker Fee: $4 per day per person after the first
